[
    {
        "index": 1,
        "start_time": 8139,
        "end_time": 11122,
        "text": "How do you know what&#39;s happening in your world?"
    },
    {
        "index": 2,
        "start_time": 11122,
        "end_time": 13621,
        "text": "The amount of information just a click away"
    },
    {
        "index": 3,
        "start_time": 13621,
        "end_time": 15281,
        "text": "may be limitless,"
    },
    {
        "index": 4,
        "start_time": 15281,
        "end_time": 17098,
        "text": "but the time and energy we have"
    },
    {
        "index": 5,
        "start_time": 17098,
        "end_time": 20233,
        "text": "to absorb and evaluate it is not."
    },
    {
        "index": 6,
        "start_time": 20233,
        "end_time": 23148,
        "text": "All the information in the world won&#39;t be very useful"
    },
    {
        "index": 7,
        "start_time": 23148,
        "end_time": 25988,
        "text": "unless you know how to read the news."
    },
    {
        "index": 8,
        "start_time": 25988,
        "end_time": 27538,
        "text": "To your grandparents, parents,"
    },
    {
        "index": 9,
        "start_time": 27538,
        "end_time": 29319,
        "text": "or even older siblings,"
    },
    {
        "index": 10,
        "start_time": 29319,
        "end_time": 31601,
        "text": "this idea would have sounded strange."
    },
    {
        "index": 11,
        "start_time": 31601,
        "end_time": 34867,
        "text": "Only a few decades ago, news was broad-based."
    },
    {
        "index": 12,
        "start_time": 34867,
        "end_time": 36203,
        "text": "Your choices were limited"
    },
    {
        "index": 13,
        "start_time": 36203,
        "end_time": 38390,
        "text": "to a couple of general interest magazines"
    },
    {
        "index": 14,
        "start_time": 38390,
        "end_time": 39968,
        "text": "and newspaper of record,"
    },
    {
        "index": 15,
        "start_time": 39968,
        "end_time": 42825,
        "text": "and three or four TV networks"
    },
    {
        "index": 16,
        "start_time": 42825,
        "end_time": 45697,
        "text": "where trusted newscasters delivered the day&#39;s news"
    },
    {
        "index": 17,
        "start_time": 45697,
        "end_time": 48901,
        "text": "at the same reliable time every evening."
    },
    {
        "index": 18,
        "start_time": 48901,
        "end_time": 51148,
        "text": "But the problems with this system soon became apparent"
    },
    {
        "index": 19,
        "start_time": 51148,
        "end_time": 53213,
        "text": "as mass media spread."
    },
    {
        "index": 20,
        "start_time": 53213,
        "end_time": 54991,
        "text": "While it was known that authoritarian countries"
    },
    {
        "index": 21,
        "start_time": 54991,
        "end_time": 57256,
        "text": "controlled and censored information,"
    },
    {
        "index": 22,
        "start_time": 57256,
        "end_time": 59665,
        "text": "a series of scandals showed that"
    },
    {
        "index": 23,
        "start_time": 59665,
        "end_time": 63211,
        "text": "democratic governments were also misleading the public,"
    },
    {
        "index": 24,
        "start_time": 63211,
        "end_time": 66058,
        "text": "often with media cooperation."
    },
    {
        "index": 25,
        "start_time": 66058,
        "end_time": 69267,
        "text": "Revelations of covert wars, secret assassinations,"
    },
    {
        "index": 26,
        "start_time": 69267,
        "end_time": 71068,
        "text": "and political corruption"
    },
    {
        "index": 27,
        "start_time": 71068,
        "end_time": 73864,
        "text": "undermined public faith in official narratives"
    },
    {
        "index": 28,
        "start_time": 73864,
        "end_time": 76793,
        "text": "presented by mainstream sources."
    },
    {
        "index": 29,
        "start_time": 76793,
        "end_time": 79421,
        "text": "This breakdown of trust in media gatekeepers"
    },
    {
        "index": 30,
        "start_time": 79421,
        "end_time": 83744,
        "text": "lead to alternative newspapers, radio shows, and cable news"
    },
    {
        "index": 31,
        "start_time": 83744,
        "end_time": 86666,
        "text": "competing with the major outlets and covering events"
    },
    {
        "index": 32,
        "start_time": 86666,
        "end_time": 88541,
        "text": "from various perspectives."
    },
    {
        "index": 33,
        "start_time": 88541,
        "end_time": 91066,
        "text": "More recently, the Internet has multiplied the amount"
    },
    {
        "index": 34,
        "start_time": 91066,
        "end_time": 92953,
        "text": "of information and viewpoints,"
    },
    {
        "index": 35,
        "start_time": 92953,
        "end_time": 95957,
        "text": "with social media, blogs, and online video"
    },
    {
        "index": 36,
        "start_time": 95957,
        "end_time": 99471,
        "text": "turning every citizen into a potential reporter."
    },
    {
        "index": 37,
        "start_time": 99471,
        "end_time": 101913,
        "text": "But if everyone is a reporter, nobody is,"
    },
    {
        "index": 38,
        "start_time": 101913,
        "end_time": 103720,
        "text": "and different sources may disagree,"
    },
    {
        "index": 39,
        "start_time": 103720,
        "end_time": 106813,
        "text": "not only opinions, but on the facts themselves."
    },
    {
        "index": 40,
        "start_time": 106813,
        "end_time": 110204,
        "text": "So how do you get the truth, or something close?"
    },
    {
        "index": 41,
        "start_time": 110204,
        "end_time": 112929,
        "text": "One of the best ways is to get the original news"
    },
    {
        "index": 42,
        "start_time": 112929,
        "end_time": 115140,
        "text": "unfiltered by middlemen."
    },
    {
        "index": 43,
        "start_time": 115140,
        "end_time": 118012,
        "text": "Instead of articles interpreting a scientific study"
    },
    {
        "index": 44,
        "start_time": 118012,
        "end_time": 119597,
        "text": "or a politician&#39;s speech,"
    },
    {
        "index": 45,
        "start_time": 119597,
        "end_time": 123423,
        "text": "you can often find the actual material and judge for yourself."
    },
    {
        "index": 46,
        "start_time": 123423,
        "end_time": 126983,
        "text": "For current events, follow reporters on social media."
    },
    {
        "index": 47,
        "start_time": 126983,
        "end_time": 129019,
        "text": "During major events, such as the Arab Spring"
    },
    {
        "index": 48,
        "start_time": 129019,
        "end_time": 130671,
        "text": "or the Ukrainian protests,"
    },
    {
        "index": 49,
        "start_time": 130671,
        "end_time": 134271,
        "text": "newscasters and bloggers have posted updates and recordings"
    },
    {
        "index": 50,
        "start_time": 134271,
        "end_time": 136434,
        "text": "from the midst of the chaos."
    },
    {
        "index": 51,
        "start_time": 136434,
        "end_time": 139416,
        "text": "Though many of these later appear in articles or broadcasts,"
    },
    {
        "index": 52,
        "start_time": 139416,
        "end_time": 141890,
        "text": "keep in mind that these polished versions"
    },
    {
        "index": 53,
        "start_time": 141890,
        "end_time": 144634,
        "text": "often combine the voice of the person who was there"
    },
    {
        "index": 54,
        "start_time": 144634,
        "end_time": 147311,
        "text": "with the input of editors who weren&#39;t."
    },
    {
        "index": 55,
        "start_time": 147311,
        "end_time": 149392,
        "text": "At the same time, the more chaotic the story,"
    },
    {
        "index": 56,
        "start_time": 149392,
        "end_time": 152369,
        "text": "the less you should try to follow it in real time."
    },
    {
        "index": 57,
        "start_time": 152369,
        "end_time": 155721,
        "text": "In events like terrorist attacks and natural disasters,"
    },
    {
        "index": 58,
        "start_time": 155721,
        "end_time": 157977,
        "text": "today&#39;s media attempts continuous coverage"
    },
    {
        "index": 59,
        "start_time": 157977,
        "end_time": 161578,
        "text": "even when no reliable new information is available,"
    },
    {
        "index": 60,
        "start_time": 161578,
        "end_time": 164141,
        "text": "sometimes leading to incorrect information"
    },
    {
        "index": 61,
        "start_time": 164141,
        "end_time": 167150,
        "text": "or false accusations of innocent people."
    },
    {
        "index": 62,
        "start_time": 167150,
        "end_time": 169842,
        "text": "It&#39;s easy to be anxious in such events,"
    },
    {
        "index": 63,
        "start_time": 169842,
        "end_time": 172152,
        "text": "but try checking for the latest information"
    },
    {
        "index": 64,
        "start_time": 172152,
        "end_time": 173991,
        "text": "at several points in the day,"
    },
    {
        "index": 65,
        "start_time": 173991,
        "end_time": 175898,
        "text": "rather than every few minutes,"
    },
    {
        "index": 66,
        "start_time": 175898,
        "end_time": 178704,
        "text": "allowing time for complete details to emerge"
    },
    {
        "index": 67,
        "start_time": 178704,
        "end_time": 181721,
        "text": "and false reports to be refuted."
    },
    {
        "index": 68,
        "start_time": 181721,
        "end_time": 183838,
        "text": "While good journalism aims for objectivity,"
    },
    {
        "index": 69,
        "start_time": 183838,
        "end_time": 186799,
        "text": "media bias is often unavoidable."
    },
    {
        "index": 70,
        "start_time": 186799,
        "end_time": 188260,
        "text": "When you can&#39;t get the direct story,"
    },
    {
        "index": 71,
        "start_time": 188260,
        "end_time": 190844,
        "text": "read coverage in multiple outlets"
    },
    {
        "index": 72,
        "start_time": 190844,
        "end_time": 194386,
        "text": "which employ different reporters and interview different experts."
    },
    {
        "index": 73,
        "start_time": 194392,
        "end_time": 197399,
        "text": "Tuning in to various sources and noting the differences"
    },
    {
        "index": 74,
        "start_time": 197399,
        "end_time": 199445,
        "text": "lets you put the pieces together"
    },
    {
        "index": 75,
        "start_time": 199445,
        "end_time": 201464,
        "text": "for a more complete picture."
    },
    {
        "index": 76,
        "start_time": 201464,
        "end_time": 204216,
        "text": "It&#39;s also crucial to separate fact from opinion."
    },
    {
        "index": 77,
        "start_time": 204216,
        "end_time": 207564,
        "text": "Words like think, likely, or probably"
    },
    {
        "index": 78,
        "start_time": 207564,
        "end_time": 209591,
        "text": "mean that the outlet is being careful"
    },
    {
        "index": 79,
        "start_time": 209591,
        "end_time": 211915,
        "text": "or, worse, taking a guess."
    },
    {
        "index": 80,
        "start_time": 211915,
        "end_time": 215653,
        "text": "And watch out for reports that rely on anonymous sources."
    },
    {
        "index": 81,
        "start_time": 215653,
        "end_time": 218677,
        "text": "These could be people who have little connection to the story,"
    },
    {
        "index": 82,
        "start_time": 218677,
        "end_time": 221409,
        "text": "or have an interest in influencing coverage,"
    },
    {
        "index": 83,
        "start_time": 221409,
        "end_time": 223564,
        "text": "their anonymity making them unaccountable"
    },
    {
        "index": 84,
        "start_time": 223564,
        "end_time": 225745,
        "text": "for the information they provide."
    },
    {
        "index": 85,
        "start_time": 225745,
        "end_time": 227545,
        "text": "Finally, and most importantly,"
    },
    {
        "index": 86,
        "start_time": 227545,
        "end_time": 230652,
        "text": "try to verify news before spreading it."
    },
    {
        "index": 87,
        "start_time": 230652,
        "end_time": 232473,
        "text": "While social media has enabled the truth"
    },
    {
        "index": 88,
        "start_time": 232473,
        "end_time": 233756,
        "text": "to reach us faster,"
    },
    {
        "index": 89,
        "start_time": 233756,
        "end_time": 235805,
        "text": "it&#39;s also allowed rumors to spread"
    },
    {
        "index": 90,
        "start_time": 235805,
        "end_time": 237588,
        "text": "before they can be verified"
    },
    {
        "index": 91,
        "start_time": 237588,
        "end_time": 239038,
        "text": "and falsehoods to survive"
    },
    {
        "index": 92,
        "start_time": 239038,
        "end_time": 241185,
        "text": "long after they&#39;ve been refuted."
    },
    {
        "index": 93,
        "start_time": 241185,
        "end_time": 243470,
        "text": "So, before you share that unbelievable"
    },
    {
        "index": 94,
        "start_time": 243470,
        "end_time": 245431,
        "text": "or outrageous news item,"
    },
    {
        "index": 95,
        "start_time": 245431,
        "end_time": 247828,
        "text": "do a web search to find any additional"
    },
    {
        "index": 96,
        "start_time": 247828,
        "end_time": 250986,
        "text": "information or context you might have missed"
    },
    {
        "index": 97,
        "start_time": 250986,
        "end_time": 253540,
        "text": "and what others are saying about it."
    },
    {
        "index": 98,
        "start_time": 253540,
        "end_time": 255567,
        "text": "Today, we are more free than ever"
    },
    {
        "index": 99,
        "start_time": 255567,
        "end_time": 257226,
        "text": "from the old media gatekeepers"
    },
    {
        "index": 100,
        "start_time": 257226,
        "end_time": 260052,
        "text": "who used to control the flow of information."
    },
    {
        "index": 101,
        "start_time": 260052,
        "end_time": 262478,
        "text": "But with freedom comes responsibility:"
    },
    {
        "index": 102,
        "start_time": 262478,
        "end_time": 265441,
        "text": "the responsibility to curate our own experience"
    },
    {
        "index": 103,
        "start_time": 265441,
        "end_time": 268492,
        "text": "and ensure that this flow does not become a flood,"
    },
    {
        "index": 104,
        "start_time": 268492,
        "end_time": 271847,
        "text": "leaving us less informed than before we took the plunge."
    }
]